       [-quiet]

       Displays the information about setPlaceMode parameters in  the  Innovus
       log  file  and  in the Innovus console. Displays the following informa-
       tion:

              * Parameter name

              * Current value

              * Type (Boolean, string, and so on)

              * Whether the current value was set by user

       If you do not specify a parameter, the Innovus software displays values
       for all of the setPlaceMode mode parameters.

Parameters
       <parameter_names>
              Returns information for the specified parameters. You can  spec-
              ify one or more parameters.

              See setPlaceModefor description of parameters.

       -quiet Returns the current settings for the specified parameters in Tcl
              list format only.

              If  you  specify -quiet without any parameters, the software re-
              turns the current settings of all setPlaceMode parameters in Tcl
              list format.

Examples
              * The following command returns  the  current  setting  for  the
                -place_global_place_io_pins parameter in Tcl list format:

                getPlaceMode -place_global_place_io_pins -quiet

                The software returns the following information:

                false

              * The  following  command  returns  the current settings for the
                -place_global_place_io_pins  and   -place_global_solver_effort
                parameters:

                getPlaceMode                       -place_global_place_io_pins
                -place_global_solver_effort

                The software returns the following information:

                -place_global_place_io_pins            #  enums={false  true},
                default=false

                -place_global_solver_effort high        # enums={medium high},
                default=high

                {-place_global_place_io_pins  false}  {place_global_solver_ef-
                fort high}

              * The following command returns the  current  settings  for  all
                setPlaceMode parameters in Tcl list format:

                getPlaceMode -quiet

                The software returns the following information:

                {place_design_floorplan_mode false} {place_design_refine_place
                true}  {place_detail_allow_border_pin_abut  false}  {place_de-
                tail_check_cut_spacing false} {place_detail_check_route false}
                {place_detail_color_aware_legal   false}    {place_detail_con-
                text_aware_legal    all}   {place_detail_eco_max_distance   0}
                {place_detail_eco_priority_insts      placed}       {place_de-
                tail_fixed_shifter   false}   {place_detail_hard_fence   true}
                {place_detail_honor_inst_pad         false}         {place_de-
                tail_io_pin_blockage       false}      {place_detail_legaliza-
                tion_inst_gap 0} {place_detail_max_shifter_column_depth  9999}
                {place_detail_max_shifter_depth        9999}        {place_de-
                tail_max_shifter_row_depth 9999} {place_detail_no_filler_with-
                out_implant   false}   {place_detail_pad_fixed_insts    false}
                {place_detail_preroute_as_obs {}} {place_detail_preserve_rout-
                ing    false}   {place_detail_remove_affected_routing   false}
                {place_detail_swap_eeq_cells         false}         {place_de-
                tail_use_check_drc  false}  {place_detail_use_GA_filler_groups
                false}  {place_detail_use_no_diffusion_one_site_filler  false}
                {place_detail_wire_length_opt_effort                   medium}
                {place_global_auto_blockage_in_channel                   none}
                {place_global_clock_gate_aware                           true}
                {place_global_clock_power_driven false} {place_global_cong_ef-
                fort   auto}   {place_global_enable_distributed_place   false}
                {place_global_group_flop_to_macro                       false}
                {place_global_group_flop_to_macro_level                     1}
                {place_global_group_flop_to_macro_list  {}}  {place_global_ig-
                nore_scan     true}     {place_global_ignore_spare      false}
